defaultIn Devon the academy programme has not 
defaultyet 
defaultseen an overall transformation in
default outcomes for student outcomes. For example, of the 20 secondary schools that have converted to become academies, seven saw a decline in GCSE performance in 2013 against an overall rise in performance across the county. However there are examples of except
