defaultOfsted 
defaulthave made it clear in their framework for inspecting LA school improvement services that LAs should continue to support, monitor and challenge all schools. Devon continues to do so but the arrangements for challenging academy schools judged to Require Impr
defaultovement by Ofsted are still being developed in practice. The Local Authority is aware that it can report any concerns it has regarding the performance of academies to the Secretary of State.
